Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.66,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:17705,21668}Whenever my feelings were hurt,\NI couldn't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.58,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:21668,25588}because I held a lie in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.55,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25588,29551}Time moved faster than I could react,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.59,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29551,34597}so I pulled myself away\Nfrom everything, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.64,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:34597,40645}I can't stop anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:47.61,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:41062,47610}Accepting everything, I rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.49,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49571,53491}I'll fly over all of time\Nwhile holding onto your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:53491,56995}following the trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:03.00,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56995,63001}My world becomes engulfed with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.25,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:65461,69257}A never ending sky,\Nyour never changing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.96,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:69257,72969}I want to love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.35,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:72969,79350}No matter the distance,\Nor if we are separated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.77,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:79350,82770}we are always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}Want you here tonight!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:91112,91112}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:38.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95950,98911}– See you later!\N– Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:43.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101914,103625}Hey, Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:49.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106002,109672}– Are you looking for UFOs again?\N– You don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:51.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:109881,111507}That's my business!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:55.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111716,115595}We're in the fifth grade now.\NIt's time you gave it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:00.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116179,120350}– Why? UFOs really exist.\N– How can you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:02.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120600,122226}– Sure they do!\N– They don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:03.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122435,123436}– Do!\N– Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:06.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123645,126606}-lf I say they do, they do!\N– Show me some proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:09.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126814,129275}Right, proof. The proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:13.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129484,133488}Proof, proof, proof, proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:15.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133696,135740}– I'll show you.\N– You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:19.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136324,139702}I'll show you for sure! For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:25.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140536,145708}THE UFO APPEARS!?\NA TOWN IN PANIC!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:27.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146125,147710}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:33.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148336,153466}– Good morning, Kyoko, Ryoko!\N– You saw the UFO last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:36.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153966,156636}The one in the morning paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:41.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156844,161849}Meimi, don't you read the papers?\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:46.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162225,166688}A UFO? "Several eyewitnesses\Nin Seika City."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:50.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166896,170525}It says people saw a shiny object\Nflying in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:54.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170733,174487}– That's definitely a UFO!\N– But why the city of Seika?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174904,177949}What else?\NIt's because St. Tail is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:03.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179450,183621}St. Tail is probably\Na messenger from outer space!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:08.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184205,188960}Yeah, a thief who roams\Nthe universe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:13.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189585,193548}How stupid! Who says\Nshe's a messenger from outer space?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:18.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193798,198803}– What a terrible way to put it.\N– There's no such thing as aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:23.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199178,203266}– Then what's this article about?\N– An optical illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:27.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203474,207478}It says many people saw it.\NCan you still call it an illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:31.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207687,211315}An airplane, a shooting star…\NAnyway, something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211524,213526}UFOs aren't scientific!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213735,216529}Science has yet to prove many things!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:40.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216738,220283}– Miss Haneoka, Mr. Asuka.\N– Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:44.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220616,224704}The two of you, use that energy\Nand go do your science homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225329,226789}Yes, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:58.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234839,238176}Meimi! Have you heard about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238843,240136}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:05.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241053,245099}"From the space shuttle to UFOs.\NCosmo World.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:10.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245600,250563}Popular event producer Yuji Kuroda\Nturns the Big Dome into outer space."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:14.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250980,254066}The UFO in the papers,\Na guy took a photo of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:16.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254358,256027}Wow! Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:19.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256652,259864}And that photo will be exhibited\Nat this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:22.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260072,262992}You're saying you wanna\Ngo and see it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263201,264702}Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:29.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264911,269499}If I see it, I'll know if it's real\Nor not. And tomorrow's Sunday…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:33.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269749,273419}Good idea.\NLet's go and check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:37.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273711,277924}– Well, now, is this a date?\N– Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281803,284096}Okay, we're ready. Go get Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:45.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284305,285848}Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286057,288684}– Dad, dinner's ready!\N– Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:50.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288893,290978}Is he outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:58.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295483,298903}That's strange. No one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:01.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299362,301155}Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:05.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303533,305368}Isn't this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:09.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305743,309372}Wow! It's a new magic trick, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:15.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309956,315628}This is much thinner than the piano\Ncord I used. Can't see it, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:19.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315837,319298}Ruby, don't struggle.\NDon't struggle so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:25.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322301,325012}Is she all right? Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:29.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325221,329225}Looks like the reeling mechanism\Nneeds more work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:32.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330017,332436}Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:44.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340069,344490}I said that to Seira,\Nbut this is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344740,346075}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:47.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346284,347618}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:49.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348578,349745}It's us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:55.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349954,355209}What's with the sour face?\NSorry we're not Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:58.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355459,358004}Ryoko, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:01.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358212,361841}– We heard about it, how it's a date.\N– Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:06.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362049,366304}– Can we come along?\N– Well, sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368347,370308}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:12.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370641,372810}You guys came along too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:17.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373060,377481}– This has to be enjoyed together.\N– Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:20.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377773,380234}I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390453,392747}Not very many people are in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:37.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392955,397752}This model is also cheaply made.\NThere's no detail whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:39.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397960,399879}Where's Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:44.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400171,404842}– Now that you mention it…\N– Maybe he's stuck to something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:50.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408721,410389}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:54.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410640,414810}Hey, Asuka! Let's take a look\Nat the UFO photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:08.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424153,428407}– What's this?\N-"The photos are being enlarged.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:12.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428616,432912}They will be shown on the last day\Nat the UFO summoning event."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:17.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433537,437041}There, you see? It's a fake\Nso they're delaying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:21.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437249,441337}No, they're probably having\Nan expert examine the photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:24.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441545,444090}I'll go ask someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:26.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444590,446592}Mr. Kuroda, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:30.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446759,450680}You're not drawing a crowd.\NAt this rate, we'll be in the red.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:35.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450888,455893}Don't worry, a turnout will come on\Nthe last day. No one will miss this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456102,457937}You mean that UFO photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:43.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458562,463693}Yes, it's fabulous. It's the hottest\Nconversation piece in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:49.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463985,469240}But shouldn't an expert examine it\Nbefore you show it to the public?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:53.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469490,473327}By the time we do that, the event\Nwill be over. It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473536,474829}But you—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:57.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475037,477915}My job is to gather people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:03.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478124,483087}I've planned, along with the photo,\Nan event to summon a real UFO.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:06.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483295,486799}It'll be a smash hit, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:10.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487550,490928}– Anyway, we're counting on you.\N– Just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:18.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495808,498060}It's the man in the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:24.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498644,504608}But, sir, if we enlarge the photo,\Neveryone will know that it's a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:28.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505067,508404}Stupid fool! You're talking too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508612,510531}Hey, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:35.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510740,515578}Why are you hanging around here?\NHurry up so we can see the UFO—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:40.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517455,520541}– What's wrong?\N– You're the one who stepped on—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:43.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520750,523461}The UFO model's that way.\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523669,525755}Kids nowadays are too mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526464,528257}Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:54.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531385,534180}You're talking about the UFO\Nin the papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:59.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534764,539310}Yeah. I want to see a UFO so badly,\NI always carry a camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:04.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539518,544106}But because of that,\Nmy friends make fun of me, so I…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560706,562708}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:30.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565920,570216}– Wow!\N– That's neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570883,572593}Is this some sort of hoax?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:36.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572802,576764}It's real.\NIt was even in this morning's paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:40.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576931,580559}– It's probably the same UFO.\N– Shota, you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:42.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580768,582478}Sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:45.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582686,585606}Then it was just\Na remote control airplane?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:50.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586273,590903}Yeah. I didn't expect it\Nto become such a big sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:56.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591403,596325}And then my friends took the photo\Nto Cosmo World without me knowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:57.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596534,597535}Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:00.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597743,600996}And it's going to be\Nexhibited at that event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:06.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601205,606627}– Have you asked for the photo back?\N– Yes, I did! But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:13.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608629,613175}My friends brought it in without\Nmy permission, that UFO photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:15.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613425,615177}Oh, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:21.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615386,621058}It's just the thing for this event,\Nso we're putting it on exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:26.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621267,626355}I'm sorry. It's a fake.\NSo please return it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:30.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626605,630985}Too late now. We already advertised\Nthat it'll be on exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631193,633279}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:37.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633487,637783}You better not tell anyone\Nit's a fake. They'll never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:41.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638200,641495}That's unfair. Please return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:46.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642204,646333}I'll return it to you\Nwhen the event is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:51.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649211,651714}If only I hadn't taken that photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:57.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652381,657219}I understand. Let's pray.\NI'm sure God is with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:00.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657803,660681}I see. So that's the story\Nbehind it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:06.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661348,666729}Shota regrets what he has done\Nand promises not to do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:11.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666937,671483}Okay! The thief St. Tail shall get\Nthat photo back for him.
Comment: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:11.69,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:671692,671692}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:17.69,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:677698,677698}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:22.70,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:682703,682703}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:50.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709855,710940}This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:55.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711148,715861}"Tonight I'll be stealing\Nthat UFO photo at the Big Dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:58.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716070,718447}– St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726789,729583}St. Tail is after that photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:14.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729917,734338}Yes, so we'll be taking care\Nof the security for the photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:16.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734546,736048}I can use him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:22.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737049,742429}I thought that if we could get a photo\Nto reveal St. Tail's identity…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:24.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742680,744431}What would you do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:29.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744640,749603}An event, of course. With that photo,\Ncrowds will swarm to such an event.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:34.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749812,754024}Absolutely not! To make\NSt. Tail into such a spectacle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:37.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754608,757361}Well, I'll leave the security to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:42.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757569,762157}The photograph is set\Nin that slide projector over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763242,765869}Weren't you having it enlarged?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:49.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766078,769039}There are limits to enlarging a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:52.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769248,772876}We're going to project it\Non a slide, like, bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:57.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773085,777006}Well, I've got things to prepare\Nso I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:02.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778340,782219}Who's gonna let a guy like that\Nreveal St. Tail's identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:11.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787433,791186}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:17.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796317,797943}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799653,801572}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:25.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803032,805534}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:44.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820674,824136}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:54.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831310,834313}Ladies and gentlemen,\Nwelcome to Cosmo World!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:59.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835064,839610}All of you here tonight will\Nwitness a historical event!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:04.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839818,844365}The boy who took the photo we'll\Nbe showing had these words to say:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:09.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844615,849578}"The UFO will definitely return\Nto retrieve this photo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850329,851538}There's more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:16.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851747,856794}We've been informed that St. Tail\Nmight appear to steal this photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:20.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857002,860589}Ladies and gentlemen,\Nhave you brought your cameras?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:24.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861590,864051}What scum, saying a thing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:29.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864760,869056}For those who photograph a UFO\Nor St. Tail's true identity…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:32.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869264,872059}…we have big rewards prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872267,874853}Now, let us begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:49.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886073,889868}Mr. Kuroda, there aren't\Nany rewards prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:55.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890077,895249}It'll be hard for anyone to photograph\NSt. Tail's true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:58.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895457,898419}But what if someone\Ndoes photograph her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:00.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898627,900337}I'll buy it in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:05.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900546,905509}If we have that, I'll surely be able\Nto fill the Big Dome unlike before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:10.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905717,910556}– But what about the UFO?\N– Don't get your hopes up on that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:15.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910764,915102}Didn't you say that a UFO\Nwill come to retrieve the photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:21.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915310,921150}Just an act to arouse the audience.\NAnd that photo, it looks like a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:25.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921775,925362}That's a problem!\NLet's cancel the event right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925612,927114}Hey, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:31.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927406,931368}The only one who will be criticized\Nis the boy who took the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:34.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931577,934079}We're only victims of a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:38.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934288,938709}And luck is on our side if\Na crowd gathers, am I not right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:40.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938917,940377}How could you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:48.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945174,948343}– Mommy, when is the UFO coming?\N– I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:51.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948760,951847}– It won't come, will it?\N– What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:54.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952514,954766}– Hurry up and summon the UFO!\N– Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954975,956894}This is where we end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:04.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958979,964109}It looks like our UFO has decided\Nto make a sidetrack somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:09.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964776,969615}While we're waiting for its arrival,\Nwe'll present the UFO photo—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:11.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969823,971575}It's the UFO!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:15.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971825,975996}The UFO appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:18.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976205,978248}A picture, a picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978457,980250}We can get the reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981293,982461}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983295,986507}Could it be a real UFO?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:31.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989051,991386}It's St. Tail! After her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:34.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991595,994014}Everyone! St. Tail has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:36.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994556,996433}– What?\N– St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:37.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996642,997976}Where, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:41.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998477,1001021}Hurry up and turn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:45.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001230,1005400}– No good! The switch won't connect!\N– Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005984,1007361}There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:49.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007611,1009238}She's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009446,1011740}Don't let her escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:59.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015202,1019248}– Are you all right, Asuka Jr.?\N– Never mind me, get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:00.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019581,1020874}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:04.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022668,1024878}There she is! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:06.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025337,1026838}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029591,1031593}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:22.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038308,1042145}St. Tail! This is\Nwhere the chase ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:25.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042896,1045857}– What's going on here?\N– I can't see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:30.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046567,1050028}The flash won't reach\Nfrom this far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050237,1052030}This is just fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:37.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052239,1057536}Mr. Kuroda! This is big trouble!\NA UFO has really appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:42.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058120,1062457}What are you gonna do?\NYou know there aren't any rewards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:45.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062749,1065002}– What's that?\N– Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:54.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072426,1074052}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:58.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074261,1078807}…showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082769,1084563}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:24.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100412,1104499}Well, Asuka Jr., I'll be\Nleaving with the photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:27.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105083,1107836}Darn! Don't think\NI'll let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:32.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108420,1112049}– Stop it! Let go of me!\N– I won't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:35.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112299,1115385}I can't stand this, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:40.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115636,1120223}– I'm not a—\N– Never mind! Just let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126188,1127439}Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:56.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134488,1136698}Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:19:00.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137532,1140535}That hurts. I shouldn't use\Nexperimental devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:05.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140786,1145082}Hold it! Just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:08.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145666,1148794}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:14.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150420,1154966}– Open this door! I've taken a picture!\N– Give me my reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:22.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158762,1162641}– What is your plan now, Kuroda?\N– Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:25.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162849,1165102}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:41.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177447,1181159}Hope you get a picture\Nof a real UFO next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:43.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182285,1183829}Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:49.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186873,1189876}How did you get that photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:53.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190085,1193880}– It fell from the sky.\N– From the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:58.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194673,1198719}It's a fake.\NI was in trouble because…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:02.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198927,1202931}…they forced me to have it\Nrevealed at the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:05.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203765,1205100}I see.
